15:56.738 --> 16:08.714
Did you go there because there was a guy who was saying something on Monday and then a hot new take on Tuesday and a brand new fresh thing on Wednesday, changing back and forth as it fit the times, a reed blown around in the wind?

16:09.936 --> 16:10.657
No, of course not.

