18:25.069 --> 18:27.192
No one else saw the Holy Spirit descend as a dove.

18:28.954 --> 18:36.265
In fact, the religious leaders are the ones that John the Baptist is turned to and says, you vipers who warned you to flee from the wrath that is coming, the people who should have known.

18:37.327 --> 18:40.692
No one had a clear picture than John the Baptist.

18:40.712 --> 18:47.762
